	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(center)">Office of <persName>S. HAMM &#38; CO.</persName></p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><placeName>No. 47 Warren&#45;Street</placeName>.</p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; <date>August 24th 1864</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Phil.</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">Will you please<lb/> send me to my house <placeName>No 119 East 13th St New<lb/> York</placeName> two copies of your edition of the daily prayers<lb/> with translation according to the custom of the Spanish &#38; Portuguese<lb/> Jews.  I should like them handsomely bound<lb/> in the most approved style.  Send by Express.<lb/>  Also let me know your prices for a set of<lb/> machsorim with translation&#44; also according to same<lb/> minhag and handsomely bound.</p>
				<p>I hope to have the pleasure of seeing you on<lb/> your next visit to this city &#38; remain</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">Yours Respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">Louis Spanier</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">pr <persName>E.S.</persName></p>
				<p>Please send Bill along</p>
		</body>
	</text>
